<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Creative Website</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>
  <sytle>
    *{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
background:#f4f4f4;
}

header{
position:absolute;
width:100%;
top:0;
left:0;
padding:20px 60px;
}

.navbar{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
color:white;
}

.logo{
font-size:24px;
font-weight:bold;
color:white;
}

.logo span{
color:#ff4b4b;
}

.nav-links{
display:flex;
list-style:none;
gap:30px;
}

.nav-links li{
cursor:pointer;
}

.hero{
height:90vh;
background-image:url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085");
background-size:cover;
background-position:center;
display:flex;
align-items:center;
justify-content:center;
text-align:center;
color:white;
}

.hero-content h1{
font-size:55px;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.hero-content p{
font-size:18px;
margin-bottom:30px;
}

.buttons{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:20px;
}

.btn1{
background:#ff4b4b;
border:none;
padding:12px 28px;
border-radius:25px;
color:white;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.btn2{
background:transparent;
border:2px solid white;
padding:12px 28px;
border-radius:25px;
color:white;
font-size:16px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.features{
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
gap:40px;
padding:80px 50px;
background:#f0f0f0;
}

.feature-box{
background:white;
padding:35px;
width:300px;
text-align:center;
box-shadow:0px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.feature-box h3{
margin-bottom:10px;
}
  </sytle>

<header>
<div class="navbar">

<div class="logo">lo<span>go</span></div>

<ul class="nav-links">
<li>Home</li>
<li>Pages</li>
<li>Portfolio</li>
<li>Blog</li>
<li>Contact</li>
</ul>

</div>
</header>

<section class="hero">

<div class="hero-content">

<h1>Create Amazing Websites<br>With Amazing Graphics</h1>

<p>We build modern, responsive and professional websites for businesses.</p>

<div class="buttons">
<button class="btn1">Explore More</button>
<button class="btn2">Buy Now</button>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="features">

<div class="feature-box">
<h3>Responsive Design</h3>
<p>Perfectly optimized for mobile, tablet and desktop screens.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-box">
<h3>Modern UI</h3>
<p>Clean layout with professional and attractive look.</p>
</div>

<div class="feature-box">
<h3>Fast Performance</h3>
<p>Optimized code structure for speed and SEO.</p>
</div>

</section>

</body>
</html>
